 2 percent of projected 2001 GDP. \par \par \uc2  These measures, swiftly taken, could bolster political and \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  confidence, support the rupiah, and allow a resumption of the state asset-sales program, all of which would help resuscitate relations with official creditors. \par \par \uc2  It is expected that the disinflationary impact of such a chain of events would more than offset the inflationary impact of \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  reductions. \par \par \uc2  Looking forward, it is unlikely that Indonesia will be able to bridge its 2002 \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  financing gap without a third Paris Club rescheduling. \par \par \uc2  This raises the specter of further, isolated syndicated-loan defaults to satisfy Paris Club burden-sharing stipulations, a key factor constraining Indonesia's long-term foreign currency ratings in the triple-'C' category, Standard & Poor's said. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010731dx7v0000i\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
