se matters. Citing an example, the minister said in applying for an identity card anywhere in the country, the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  may not be charged a fee in excess of the officially stipulated one. Faisal said he had also given the president inputs on a proposal that cabinet ministers not be allowed to serve concurrently as head of a state agency outside his or her ministerial realm. He noted that in the present cabinet lineup, only the Minister of State for Development Planing was also functioning as chairman of the National Development Planning Agency (Bappenas). \par \par \uc2  Civil Servants' Salaries About the question of civil servants' salaries, Faisal quoted the President as saying they had yet to be readjusted to the much increased general cost of living. But the President also indicated that under the present unfavourable \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  conditions, the government was still unable to give civil servants better salaries. She however promised to seek a solution especially to the low salaries of school teachers. About the possibility of thousands of former Social Affairs Ministry employees being rerecruited by the present Social Affairs Ministry, Faisal said Social Affairs Minister Bachtiar Chamsjah was currently designing the structure of his ministry. Soon after assuming the presidency in October 2000, President Megawati's predecessor, Abdurrahman Wahid, dissolved the then existing Social Affairs Ministry, causing tens of thousands of its employees to face an \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain\b0 \highlight\uc2  future. \par \par \uc2 Document antara0020010822dx8k0000a\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
